title: One Bedroom Upstairs, Pool & Sun Deck, BBQ Area
posting_body: ['Welcome to Pleasanton Place Apartments Homes!', 'Take a walk to historic Downtown Pleasanton.', "Here you will get to enjoy shopping in the one of a kind boutiques, dining in 4 star restaurants, getting your fresh produce at the year round farmer's market, and listening to live music in the concerts in the park.", '- 2 On-site Community Laundry Centers', '- $0 Deposit Community', '- 10-minute walk from historical Downtown Pleasanton', '- Pool with sun deck', '- Picnic area with barbeque', '- Easy access to BART, ACE Train, I-680 and I-580', '- Many options to pay rent including credit card and ACH', '- Resident referral program', '- Award winning Pleasanton school district', '- Professional management', '- Near major Tri-Valley employment centers, shopping, dining & entertainment', '- Assigned covered parking', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Pricing is subject to change.', 'Call for details.', 'Property Code PP:ESR3609']
